How I approach personal growth will have a major impact on the quality of my
life.  I am always becoming something. The key question is, "What am I 
becoming?" and "Is that where I want to go?" Every week I am either growing
better or worse.

7 "Do not judge others, and you will not be judged. 2 For you will be treated as you treat others.
3 "And why worry about a speck in your friend's eye 'Let me help you get rid of that speck in your eye,' when you can't see past the log in your own eye? 5 Hypocrite! First get rid of the log in your own eye; then you will see well enough to deal with the speck in your friend's eye.
6 "Don't waste what is holy on people who are unholy. Don't throw your pearls to pigs! They will trample the pearls, then turn and attack you.

